title: BONUS EPISODE: Tokischa On Madonna, OnlyFans, + Performances
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Dominican artist Tokischa sits down with Ebro in the Morning to allow the world to get to know her a bit more personally. She breaks down her difficult upbringing, her inspirations, how she knew she would be famous from a young anger, her decision to be free expressing her sexuality and body, and why she will continue creating content on her OnlyFans account. She also discusses her experience working with Madonna, what to expect from her performances, her music, and much more!
